        "164019308781fb4c92-0": {
          "type": "html",
          "settings": {
            "code": "<div>\n<span class=\"subtop\">The Path to Purity</span>\n<h2 class=\"text-left my-5\">Brand Story</h2>\n<p class=\"mt-4\">Something that sounds so ethereal should not be so difficult for me to obtain, right? Unfortunately, my path was disrupted by numerous obstacles and pitfalls that hindered my progress, with the education system being a prominent contributor. After discovering my passion for health and wellness, I immersed myself in studies and quickly came to realize that much of what I had been taught as a child was either false or presented an incomplete picture.\n</p>\n<p class=\"mt-4\">\nDetermined to bridge the gap between my past knowledge and the present reality, I embarked on a journey to Hawaii, where I resided for six months, fully embracing the culture around me. During this transformative period, I had the privilege of engaging with new people and practices. Natives shared their wisdom with me, revealing insights about preventative healthcare and herbalism that expanded my understanding.\n</p>\n<p class=\"mt-4\">\nThe revelation that the body holds the innate ability to heal itself when supported by natural supplements ignited a thirst for further education within me. At that juncture, I knew I needed to share this newfound awareness with others, and I was driven to devise a solution that could ultimately benefit everyone. And so, Ancient Bliss was brought into existence. Drawing inspiration from Pele, the Ancient Hawaiian Goddess of volcanoes symbolizing transformative power, Ancient Bliss was conceived with the aim of encouraging everyone to nurture themselves in the pure, wholesome manner they rightfully deserve.\n</p>\n<img src=\"\">\n</div>",
            "width": "50%",
            "align": "center"
          }
        }
      },
